data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This meticulously maintained 2-story Craftsman-style gem, built by Capshaw in 2018, is a shining example of modern elegance. From the moment you step onto the covered front porch, you'll be captivated by the charm and quality of this like-new property.    The main floor boasts a spacious and inviting layout with luxury features throughout. The oversized owner's suite on the main floor is a true retreat, offering both comfort and convenience. The ensuite bathroom features a dual vanity, ensuring a stress-free morning routine.    The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a generous amount of cabinetry. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living area, anchored by a cozy fireplace – the perfect spot for creating lasting memories with family and friends.    LVP flooring graces the entire home, providing durability and a touch of modern sophistication. Step outside to the deck, overlooking a spacious and level yard, complete with a fenced backyard for added privacy and security.    Nestled in a gated community within a highly desired area, this property offers both tranquility and security. Proximity to excellent schools and convenient shopping ensures that your family's needs are met with ease.    This home is ready for the most discerning buyer, meticulously designed and maintained to meet the highest standards. Don't wait too long – this property is sure to sell quickly! Schedule a viewing before it's too late, and make this dream home yours. You won't want to miss out on this incredible opportunity!
